        {
            "title": "6G全球高峰會在港開幕 丘應樺：正全力營造有利環境 為6G時代做好準備",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4219d69e0249e832bcf3730dd4cb7eac/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050812353757452.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>由通訊事務管理局承辦的6G全球高峰會今日（8日）起一連兩天在港舉行，商務及經濟發展局局長丘應樺表示，特區政府正全力營造有利環境，推動科技進步，為6G時代做好準備。 當局已經在提前佈局，並採取實際行動，迎接6G發展。\n\n</p>\n<p>丘應樺表示，去年 11月本港成為世界上首個拍賣6千和7千兆赫頻段無線電頻譜的城市，目前香港主要的流動網路營運商已積極進行測試，並已成功驗證5.5G技術在各項應用上的表現，包括大型無人機表演、世界級運動賽事等。\n\n</p>\n<p>他指，有關技術令本港能夠創建更智慧的互聯網絡。另外，當局亦看到發展低空經濟的巨大潛力，正積極從電訊角度探討進一步的便利措施，支持低空經濟發展。\n\n</p>\n<p>丘應樺表示，香港已實現全港5G覆蓋，用戶約800萬，佔去年總人口的105%以上，本港5G可用性在亞太地區排名第一。他指，香港具有獨特優勢，可以在6G發展中發揮主導作用，並強調本港的基礎設施為6G部署奠定堅實基礎，可體現支援尖端應用和服務的能力。\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2067856/即時-財經-6G全球高峰會在港開幕-丘應樺-正全力營造有利環境-為6G時代做好準備",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 12:42:06",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "NBA｜紐約人又落後20分反勝塞爾特人 碧捷斯連續兩場偷波致勝",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"碧捷斯(白衫25號)偷走泰頓最後一擊的傳球。AFP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/66d68539a4b81b90d3afac96c1fce3be/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050812014117822.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">碧捷斯(白衫25號)偷走泰頓最後一擊的傳球。AFP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周三NBA季後賽東岸次圈第2回合，紐約人再上演反勝好戲，繼首回合後再次落後20分下反勝，作客以91:90奏捷，場數領先2:0。紐約人球星碧捷斯更連續兩場關鍵時刻成功偷波阻止對方最後一擊，成為英雄，他直言要感謝隊友一直支持。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"碧捷斯(白衫25號)偷走泰頓最後一擊的傳球。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/347ce7b8716e398fb961f9032c6bda6e/2025-05/Knicks_Celtics_Basketball_03899--6b427.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        碧捷斯(白衫25號)偷走泰頓最後一擊的傳球。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"碧捷斯(白衫25號)偷走泰頓最後一擊的傳球。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c78cf52707e10025d3d06ce721c3888e/2025-05/AFP__20250508__2213338167__v1__HighRes__2025NbaPlayoffsNewYorkKnicksVBostonCelticsGa.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        碧捷斯(白衫25號)偷走泰頓最後一擊的傳球。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"碧捷斯(白衫25號)。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/611f5664a7e5a0b0cacae684a8b43302/2025-05/2025-05-08T014843Z_2062554987_MT1USATODAY26118135_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PLAYOFFS-NEW-YORK-KNICKS-AT-BOSTON-CELTICS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        碧捷斯(白衫25號)。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"碧捷斯(白衫25號)。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a547430710df3e0afee0a92be6f60711/2025-05/2025-05-08T014651Z_195213785_MT1USATODAY26118125_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PLAYOFFS-NEW-YORK-KNICKS-AT-BOSTON-CELTICS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        碧捷斯(白衫25號)。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"碧捷斯(白衫25號)。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0a3a2666de5c1f47652f81bc4efa5ddc/2025-05/2025-05-08T001231Z_1678802314_MT1USATODAY26117039_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PLAYOFFS-NEW-YORK-KNICKS-AT-BOSTON-CELTICS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        碧捷斯(白衫25號)。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"碧捷斯(白衫25號)。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7adcbc6bed5678c812306c848b8b044/2025-05/Knicks_Celtics_Basketball_52533--12d6f.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        碧捷斯(白衫25號)。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"紐約人反勝塞爾特人。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d715e073c24d2b1608a6a29c5c415e9d/2025-05/Knicks_Celtics_Basketball_47283--03f4b.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        紐約人反勝塞爾特人。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"紐約人反勝塞爾特人。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c72230ce762b251507138f42f95a31e3/2025-05/Knicks_Celtics_Basketball_81408--27cc7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        紐約人反勝塞爾特人。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"紐約人反勝塞爾特人。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a85486d7fdfc28e207ca9fcc3565436/2025-05/Knicks_Celtics_Basketball_36264--f1f6e.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        紐約人反勝塞爾特人。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>紐約人又落後20分反勝</h2>\n<p>首回合紐約人在一度落後20分下力戰至加時後以108:105反勝塞爾特人。綠軍今仗再次入局較快，並於第3節中段又領先達20分，且一直未落後過。然而，綠軍於第4節一度8分鐘內未於運動戰得分，被紐約人打出一段21:2的攻勢反超前，最終以91:90反勝，成為近25年首支連續2場作客克服落後20分劣勢反勝的球隊，場數領先2:0。\n\n</p><h2>碧捷斯又做英雄</h2>\n<p>紐約人上場靠碧捷斯成功偷波阻止綠軍最後一擊奠勝，今場第4節他又擔當關鍵角色。頭3節他一分未得，但末節獨取14分助球隊後上，而且綠軍的最後一擊同樣被他偷波終結。此子賽後喜言：「最後一次成功防守全靠隊友的努力。感謝他們一直支持我，由我原本一球不進開始直到最後，是他們幫我穩住心態，讓我保持清醒，不斷鼓勵我繼續堅持下去。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2067846/即時-體育-NBA-紐約人又落後20分反勝塞爾特人-碧捷斯連續兩場偷波致勝",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 12:36:43",
